title: Refrigerator Torsion-Fit Spring
description: Refrigerator Torsion-Fit Spring ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 1 Review PartSelect Number PS2374786 Manufacturer Part Number WR49X10233 This part is the replacement torsion-fit spring for your refrigerator. It is made of metal and is sold individually. The torsion-fit spring provides tension to return the ice funnel back to its normal position after it dispenses ice. If your refrigerator is not dispensing ice or water properly, you may need to replace the torsion-fit spring. This is an OEM part sourced directly from the manufacturer.

installationInstructions.author: carl from vacaville, CA
installationInstructions.title: ice and water would not dispense at door
installationInstructions.content: first I snapped out control face plate on outside of door. removed the screws for each part,and unplugged the wires at the connectors, replaced new parts and plugged in connectors to new circuit board.I decided to replace the board,switch and solenoid all at the same time, not knowing which part was bad.I have to say it was well worth it! it works better than when it was new!!!! It was a lot easier than I thought it was going to be.
